docs.text:
vfs documentation


Dispatcher


The dispatcher instantiates VFS instances from URL and caches instances for better performance.


URL are parsed with Node.js' 
url
 module, the positional options to 
url.parse
 can be provided as options.


dispatcher
.
parseUrl
(
sftp:///?q=xs
,
 
{
slashesDenoteHost
:
 
true
,
 
parseQueryString
:
 
false
})
